# ── EmailJS (https://www.emailjs.com → Account → API Keys) ───────────────────
# EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID  → Email Services → tu servicio (ej. service_xxxxxxx)
# EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID → Email Templates → tu plantilla (ej. template_xxxxxxx)
# EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY  → Account → Public Key
# EMAILJS_PRIVATE_KEY → Account → Private Key  (requerido para llamadas server-side)
